  "title": "Marketing and Sales Leader",
  "description": "<h2><strong>✨ Marketing and Sales Leader ✨</strong></h2><p><strong>(Excellent Career Growth | Travel Incentives | Supportive Team)</strong></p><p><strong>About the Role</strong></p><p>We are looking for energetic and creative individuals to join our growing team. If you enjoy meeting people, working in dynamic environments, and being part of exciting brand campaigns, this opportunity is perfect for you.</p><h3>⭐ What You Will Do</h3><ul><li>Be the face of global brands at exciting roadshows, events, and promotions.</li><li>Engage with the public to create positive and memorable brand experiences.</li><li>Work closely with a vibrant team to achieve and exceed campaign targets.</li><li>Assist with on-site event logistics, setup, and customer interaction.</li><li>Learn and apply direct marketing and customer engagement techniques.</li></ul><h3>⭐ What We Offer</h3><ul><li><strong>Clear career growth opportunities</strong> into Team Leader and management roles.</li><li><strong>Travel exposure </strong>for top performers, including local and overseas incentives.</li><li>A dynamic, fun, and <strong>supportive team environment</strong>.</li><li>Comprehensive <strong>1-to-1 training</strong> and coaching—no experience needed.</li></ul><h3>⭐ Who We Are Looking For</h3><ul><li>A positive, confident, and outgoing personality.</li><li>Enjoys interacting with people and is a natural team player.</li><li>Willing to learn, hardworking, and open to new challenges.</li><li>No prior experience required—full training will be provided.</li></ul><h3>Ready to Join Us?</h3><p>If you're someone who loves a vibrant workplace, seeks real growth, and enjoys connecting with people, we would love to meet you.</p><p><strong>ARE YOU A THRIVER? Apply now with your resume!</strong></p><p><strong>#WhyThrive #ReadyToThrive</strong></p>",
